| StringGetHashcode |  modified |       0 - 8 |   610.1 us |  8.423 us |  7.879 us |   606.7 us |  0.84 |    0.02 |
|                   |           |             |            |           |           |            |       |         |
| **StringGetHashcode** |  **baseline** |      **6 - 24** |   **982.7 us** |  **8.118 us** |  **7.196 us** |   **982.3 us** |  **1.00** |    **0.00** |
| StringGetHashcode |  modified |      6 - 24 |   830.4 us |  7.423 us |  6.580 us |   830.2 us |  0.85 |    0.01 |
|                   |           |             |            |           |           |            |       |         |
| **StringGetHashcode** |  **baseline** |     **20 - 96** | **2,629.6 us** | **55.359 us** | **84.539 us** | **2,587.3 us** |  **1.00** |    **0.00** |
| StringGetHashcode |  modified |     20 - 96 | 2,425.9 us | 29.657 us | 27.741 us | 2,420.3 us |  0.90 |    0.03 |
